OL,3,CCost of childcare forces parents to
OL,4,Cconsider leaving island
OL,6,FParents in Jersey say they are having
OL,7,Fto consider leaving the island due to
OL,8,Fthe high price of childcare.
OL,10,FFull-time nursery fees are around
OL,11,F#23,000 a year for babies and toddlers
OL,12,Fup to the age of two, almost double
OL,13,Fthe average price in England, which is
OL,14,F#12,425.
OL,16,FMother Marijcke Klynsmith explains how
OL,17,Fhigh childcare costs were a key factor
OL,18,Fin her choosing to step away from her
OL,19,Fcareer: "It caused us to say, 'Ok,
OL,20,Flet's just stop work completely'".
