OL,6,FEven so, she says she may have to
OL,7,Freturn to South Africa to be near
OL,8,Ffamily.
OL,10,FMarijcke adds: "I think our long-term
OL,11,Fplan is actually leaving - it's sad as
OL,12,Fwe really love Jersey, but it's much
OL,13,Fcheaper and loads more to do with the
OL,14,Fmoney that you have."
OL,16,FOthers say high costs are driving
OL,17,Ftheir decisions on whether to have
OL,18,Fchildren altogether.
