OL,6,FMother Yasmin Logan says: "I know
OL,7,Fpeople that would love to have a
OL,8,Fsecond child but they just can't
OL,9,Fbecause they're trying to make ends
OL,10,Fmeet as it is ... it's not doable for
OL,11,Flots of people."
OL,13,FThe Government of Jersey currently
OL,14,Foffers 30 hours of free nursery
OL,15,Feducation every week in the year a
OL,16,Fchild turns four, during term time.
OL,18,FSkye is a mother of three and when she
OL,19,Fbecame pregnant, her mother took a
OL,20,Fcareer break to help with childcare.
