OL,3,CCost of childcare forces parents to
OL,4,Cconsider leaving island
OL,6,FSkye explains: "We wouldn't have been
OL,7,Fable to afford childcare at all. It
OL,8,Fwould have been more than my husband
OL,9,Fearns.
OL,11,F"In this day and age, a lot of those
OL,12,Fgrandparents will still be in work and
OL,13,Fstill be professionals, with their own
OL,14,Ffinancial pressures."
OL,16,FThe Jersey Childcare Trust thinks this
OL,17,Fis a contributing factor to falling
OL,18,Fbirth rates locally - it dropped to
OL,19,Fits lowest level in 80 years in 2024.
