OL,3,CCost of childcare forces parents to
OL,4,Cconsider leaving island
OL,6,FExecutive Director Fiona Vacher says:
OL,7,F"I think parents are in a catch-22. Do
OL,8,Fthey return to work with the enormous
OL,9,Fcosts of childcare, or do they stay at
OL,10,Fhome for a little period of time and
OL,11,Fcare for their child, but face housing
OL,12,Fand other living costs as well? It's a
OL,13,Fvery difficult balance for them."
OL,15,FIn response, Deputy Andy Howell, the
OL,16,FAssistant Minister for Health and
OL,17,FSocial Services, says: "I do
OL,18,Funderstand for them it's a bit of a
OL,19,Fjuggle but I think our government are
OL,20,Faware and are doing all we can to make
OL,21,Fit better for people."
